# Project Overview - Tutti Dashboard

This is a React-based admin dashboard UI built with modern web technologies, focusing on responsiveness and accessibility.

## Project Purpose
- Tutti Dashboard UI crafted with ShadcnUI and Vite
- Built with responsiveness and accessibility in mind
- Reusable collection of dashboard UI components for future projects
- Features 10+ pages with custom components

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: React 19 with TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: [Vite](mdc:vite.config.ts) with SWC
- **UI Library**: ShadcnUI (TailwindCSS + RadixUI)
- **Routing**: TanStack Router with [routeTree.gen.ts](mdc:src/routeTree.gen.ts)
- **State Management**: Zustand stores + TanStack Query
- **Styling**: TailwindCSS v4
- **Icons**: Tabler Icons + Lucide React
- **Forms**: React Hook Form with Zod validation
- **Testing/Quality**: ESLint, Prettier, TypeScript, Knip

## Key Features
- Light/dark theme switching
- Responsive design
- Accessibility focused
- Built-in Sidebar component
- Global Search Command
- Authentication system
- Form handling with validation

